k externality degree is larger than the average device valuation,\nwhich is in stark contrast with the connectivity service model in which hybrid\npricing always outperforms bundled pricing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Mar 2018 15:49:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-21"}
